{"tid":27883,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]SD card唔小心格式化左...","createTime":"2016-12-07T15:10:43.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T19:24:34.000Z","uid":59336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"16761cf35d854c92f48df3d48ad6c36002944625","tid":27883,"uid":59336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:10:43.000Z","msg":"錯手格式化左張SD CARD <br />\n入面有40GB, 分左好多個folders分晒類 <br />\n想問下有無software係可以跟返原本個folder分類去recover返? <br />\n我見好多software都只係打散晒幫你recover返 <br />\n因為入面有&gt;10000個files, 打散晒都唔知點樣執得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n張卡用左唔夠半年應該無壞 <br />\n格式化左之後都無擺野入去 <br />\n就算唔係免費software都唔緊要 <br />\n最緊要係可以跟folder去recover<br />\n<br />\n已經拎過出去俾人整但d files都係散晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n賜油!!"},{"pid":"da4bfeb305fee88d31395523a68e2f48dabde432","tid":27883,"uid":59336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T19:59:10.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f858679c5200d81018616303e1cf85a1cd1c6da","tid":27883,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:58:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ntestdisk  係成個 directory recover"},{"pid":"877f39ecc433e6b94e246e582d4d9093d4a5e64c","tid":27883,"uid":50329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:57:33.000Z","msg":"應該好難<br />\n應該唔係一般網上 download 到既 software 做到<br />\n應該要搵專業既 lab 做，咁會好貴"},{"pid":"7b3ad9121f792405d9601